    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >玩沙子</h2>《沙盒中的沙子》是一个动态的落沙模拟器，你可以在其中使用沙子、水、盐、酸等多种材料玩耍。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225680/extras/f9fd20de6b430d29a1516d8e7e721a62.poster.avif?t=1732027750\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225680/extras/f9fd20de6b430d29a1516d8e7e721a62.webm?t=1732027750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225680/extras/f9fd20de6b430d29a1516d8e7e721a62.mp4?t=1732027750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >热成像视图</h2>使用热成像视图探索模拟中的热力学动态。此功能帮助你直观理解不同材料之间的热量传递。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225680/extras/0798b86d7936736275ef04de9922617a.poster.avif?t=1732027750\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225680/extras/0798b86d7936736275ef04de9922617a.webm?t=1732027750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225680/extras/0798b86d7936736275ef04de9922617a.mp4?t=1732027750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >电导率</h2>在你的沙盒中利用电力。通过金属传导电力，并观察它与其他元素的互动，例如使用电加热器煮沸水。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225680/extras/d5777f99e2791b3ebbc1bb5e07df2989.poster.avif?t=1732027750\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225680/extras/d5777f99e2791b3ebbc1bb5e07df2989.webm?t=1732027750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225680/extras/d5777f99e2791b3ebbc1bb5e07df2989.mp4?t=1732027750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >放射性</h2>试验放射性材料。管理并观察元素的衰变及其对周围材料的影响。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225680/extras/881729aaf0b6f97c0f9a9fc04060b365.poster.avif?t=1732027750\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225680/extras/881729aaf0b6f97c0f9a9fc04060b365.webm?t=1732027750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225680/extras/881729aaf0b6f97c0f9a9fc04060b365.mp4?t=1732027750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >模组功能</h2>通过广泛的模组支持增强你的游戏体验。创建并分享你自己的自定义元素。根据自己的喜好修改游戏规则，并通过社区驱动的平台探索无限可能性。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225680/extras/4178193d81e0042a3760d63438dc3bf6.poster.avif?t=1732027750\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225680/extras/4178193d81e0042a3760d63438dc3bf6.webm?t=1732027750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225680/extras/4178193d81e0042a3760d63438dc3bf6.mp4?t=1732027750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
